div.div: Tired of the yoke of the Divine Justice Alliance, master assassin Cheon Ha-Jin attempts to flee, only to be confronted by martial artists of all allegiances, both orthodox and deviant. Succumbing to the wounds of his ferocious struggle for freedom, he awakens in the body of Seo Ryang, a prince of the notorious Heavenly Demon Cult who suffers from a disorder that prohibits him from the use of qi. In order to survive in his new life, Ha-Jin must contend with the many dangers and enemies that lurk within the cult. (Source: WEBTOONS, edited)

The Wanjie Continent is filled with prodigies, acclaimed as deities, princes, and taoists, representing the future of each sect. The untalented and ordinary Qin Shu was supposed to one of these prodigies due to his father, one of the strongest men on the continent. But instead he was looked down and jeered upon by everyone in his sect. Until one day, his Wanjie Checkin System finally reached 100%, and all of a sudden he reached peak power by unlocking the skill of Perpetual Dantian!
(Source: Tencent, translated)
